"Beware of weird encounter." Oh, that wasn't it? Ok. Dude swoops up YELLING about how I'm beautiful & he needs a hug. I put my hand in his face & said no. He looked surprised. Lmfao. He backed away. I heard, "there's more."

#angelmessage

She told me years ago I would "run into" him. His career and that we will marry in 2023. Described him well. Fuck my life b/c I literally walked into a cop! I can't right now. Of course I ran away. We kept finding each other. He was working. I'm gonna rest, lol. Smh. ğŸ‘®
